<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your profile</title>
</head>
<body>
    {{> headerTrue}}
    <div>
        <form action="/api/myPage/profile_method=PUT" method="POST">
            <span>name: </span><input type="text" name="name" value="{{name}}" required>
            <span>surname: </span><input type="text" name="surname" value="{{surname}}" required>
            <label for="">Your email: {{email}}</label>
            <span>age: </span> <input type="number" name="age" value="{{age}}">
            <span>country: </span> <input type="text" name="country" value="{{country}}">
            <label for="">experience</label>
            <p>Write main information about your experince in programming.</p>
            <textarea name="exerience" cols="30" rows="5">{{experience}}</textarea>
            <label for="">links</label>
            <p>Write some links abbot you if you want in such format as: git - http:/git/somepage/yourAccount. </p>
            <p>Put an enter after every link.</p>
            <textarea name="links" cols="30" rows="5">{{links}}</textarea>
            <span>phone: </span><input type="tel" name="phone" value="{{phone}}">
            <label for="">other</label>
            <p>Write details that you also want to tell.</p>
            <textarea name="other" cols="30" rows="10">{{other}}</textarea>
            <input type="submit" value="Update">
        </form>
    </div>
    {{> footer}}
</body>
</html>